data.description: This 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms home provides ample space for comfortable living featuring a bonus den or office space. The spacious living areas create a welcoming atmosphere, complemented by hardwood floors throughout. The updated kitchen features new granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. As winter nights approach, cozy up by the fireplace. Step outside to your own private backyard oasis featuring a hot tub, offering a serene retreat for relaxation or outdoor entertaining. Convenient parking is ensured with the detached garage. Just blocks away from the picturesque Minnehaha Falls. This home offers not only a prime location but also thoughtful features that make it a great place to call home.
